{"name": "easysemver", "metadata": {"name": "easysemver", "version": "0.2.0", "classifiers": [], "home_page": "https://github.com/azimuth-cloud/easysemver", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "Simple semver utilities for Python.", "upload_time": 1722421035}, "documentation": ["# easysemver\n\nThis package provides utilities for comparing [SemVer](https://semver.org/) versions,\nwith special attention on the correct treatment of prerelease parts.\n\n## Installation\n\n`easysemver` can be installed from PyPI:\n\n```sh\npip install easysemver\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nBefore versions can be compared, they must be converted into `Version` objects. If the version\nis not valid SemVer, a `TypeError` will be raised.\n\n```python\nfrom easysemver import Version\n\n# Not a valid SemVer version, so raises TypeError\nversion = Version(\"20230809-1\")\n# Create a SemVer version\nversion = Version(\"1.2.3\")\n# Prerelease and build parts are supported\nversion = Version(\"1.2.3-alpha.0+abcdefg\")\n\n# Comparing versions respects prerelease parts\n#   The following all resolve to True\nVersion(\"1.2.3\") < Version(\"1.2.4\")\nVersion(\"1.2.3\") < Version(\"2.0.0\")\nVersion(\"1.2.3\") < Version(\"1.2.4-alpha.0\")\nVersion(\"1.2.3-alpha.0\") < Version(\"1.2.3\")\n#   Prerelease parts that are all digits are compared as numbers\nVersion(\"1.2.3-alpha.0\") < Version(\"1.2.3-alpha.100\")\n#   Prerelease parts that are strings are compared as strings\nVersion(\"1.2.3-alpha.0\") < Version(\"1.2.3-beta.0\")\n#   Note that build parts don't affect comparison\nVersion(\"1.2.3\") == Version(\"1.2.3+abcdefg\")\n```\n\nVersions can also be compared to a SemVer range, which consists of a number of constraints\nseparated by commas. Similar to `Version`, a `TypeError` will be raised if the constraints\nare not valid.\n\nThe supported constraints are SemVer versions with an operator, where the supported operators\nare `==`, `!=`, `>=`, `>`, `<=` and `<`.\n\n```python\nfrom easysemver import Range, Version\n\n# Resolves to True\nVersion(\"1.2.3\") in Range(\">=1.0.0,<2.0.0\")\n# Resolves to False\nVersion(\"1.2.3\") in Range(\">=2.0.0\")\n# Prerelease versions are only considered part of a range if the lower bound includes a prerelease part\n#   Resolves to False\nVersion(\"1.2.3-alpha.0\") in Range(\">=1.0.0\")\n#\u00a0  Resolves to True\nVersion(\"1.2.3-alpha.0\") in Range(\">=1.0.0-0\")\n# Specific versions can be exclulded\n#   Resolves to False\nVersion(\"1.2.3\") in Range(\">=1.0.0,<2.0.0,!=1.2.3\")\n#\u00a0  Resolves to True\nVersion(\"1.2.4\") in Range(\">=1.0.0,<2.0.0,!=1.2.3\")\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "easysemver", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "easysemver.Range", "xref": {"fqname": "easysemver.main.Range", "project": null}}, {"name": "easysemver.SEMVER_RANGE_REGEX", "xref": {"fqname": "easysemver.main.SEMVER_RANGE_REGEX", "project": null}}, {"name": "easysemver.SEMVER_VERSION_REGEX", "xref": {"fqname": "easysemver.main.SEMVER_VERSION_REGEX", "project": null}}, {"name": "easysemver.Version", "xref": {"fqname": "easysemver.main.Version", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "easysemver.main", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "easysemver.main.SEMVER_VERSION_REGEX", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.SEMVER_VERSION_ANY_REGEX", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.SEMVER_CONSTRAINT_REGEX", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.SEMVER_CONSTRAINT_ANY_REGEX", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.SEMVER_RANGE_REGEX", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "easysemver.main.Component", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "easysemver.main.Component.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "value", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Component.__eq__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "other", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Component.__gt__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "other", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Component.__str__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Component.increment", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Represents a component in a version."]}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Version", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "easysemver.main.Version.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "version", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Version.format", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "prefix", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "prerelease", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "build", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Version.__str__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Version.__eq__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "other", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Version.__gt__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "other", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Version.bump_major", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "preserve_build", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Version.bump_minor", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "preserve_build", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Version.bump_patch", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "preserve_build", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Represents a SemVer version."]}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Constraint", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "easysemver.main.Constraint.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "operator", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "version", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Constraint.__contains__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "version", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Constraint.is_upper", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Constraint.is_lower", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Constraint.__str__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Constraint.expand", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cls", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "constraint", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Represents a single SemVer constraint."]}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Range", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "easysemver.main.Range.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "range", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Range.__contains__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "version", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easysemver.main.Range.__str__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Represents a SemVer range consisting of the union of multiple constraints."]}], "exports": []}]}